;How Lightbeam Works
Como functiona Lightbeam


;Download and run the Lightbeam add-on in your Firefox browser.
Discarga e usa Lightbeam addition a tu navigator Firefox.


;Lightbeam will create a record of events for every site you visit and every third party site that is stored locally on your browser.
Lightbeam creara un registro del eventos pro cata sito que tu visita e cata sito de tertie parte que es salvate localmente sur tu navigator.


;Lightbeam visually graphs these events to highlight the interactions between sites you intentionally visit and the third parties.
Lightbeam visualisa le graphicos de iste eventos pro evidentiar le interactiones inter le sitos que tu vole visitar e los de tertie partes.


;Lightbeam will continue to add to your graph as you browse the Web. You can stop Lightbeam at any time by disabling it or uninstalling the add-on. Your Lightbeam data can be easily saved or deleted.
Lightbeam continuara a adder a tu graphico durante que tu explora le Web. Tu pote abolir Lightbeam aliquando per lo disactivar o disinstallar su additivo. Tu pote abolir Lightbeam aliquando per lo disactivar o disinstallar le additivo.


;Tracking & privacy
Traciamento e confidentialitate


;Not all tracking is bad. Many services rely on user data to provide relevant content and enhance your online experience.
Non tote le traciamentos es mal. Plure servicios fide sur datos de usatores pro fornir contento pertinente e meliorar tu experientia de Internet.


;But tracking can happen without the user’s knowledge.
Ma le traciamento pote occurrer sin cognoscentia del usator.


;That’s not okay for some.
Unes non pote acceptar isto.


;It should be you who decides when, how and if you want your browsing data to be shared. We recognize the importance of transparency and our mission is all about empowering users — both with tools and information.
Debe esser tu qui decide quando, como e si tu desira que tu datos de navigation es compartite. Nos recognosce le gravitate del transparentia e nostre mission es tote pro potentiar le usatores — sia per instrumentos, sia per informationes.


;We’re building this crowd-sourced directory to encourage users to visualize the state of tracking as an aggregate and to examine relationships that exist on the Web.
Nos crea iste directorio per contributiones massive pro incoragiar le usatores a visualisar syntheticamente le stato de traciamento, e a compulsar le parentatos que existe sur le Web.


;Visualize your data
